{"tid":1448192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:34:16.000Z","uid":96660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a4f2a82d081355f29128021e0d8dd5c9f0f207","tid":1448192,"uid":96660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=e8ea8232\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=33d16f7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"99fdbcb388beb5314c7b6212de52375f32c065d2","tid":1448192,"uid":96660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43895a39c3f21b7da16f1f6b0c09b7f33678b2ec","tid":1448192,"uid":96660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cb2ba7560501919fd57adc417359c9e06ebca0","tid":1448192,"uid":96660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4893a9908c519ce9f